settings.description: Embarking a Journey on the First Unused level but It's Improved by a little bit, Good luck finding the hidden Ace coins!

So I made the first level of TI2,a SMBX map.
I don't know what's wrong but a gap appears in the bouns room and i cant remove it,then I place a pipe to cover it.Hovever,have fun :)
NEED RAIN OR SNOWED IS JANUARY
Fun Fact: I'm terrible at making underwater levels, so I just decided to take out the water in the underwater, thus creating an... under level.
Honestly loosely based on one level from the SMBX game 'the invasion 2', for remember a level with the hammer bros themes and mario bros elements? well... here I'm trying to go for that theme!
strange spinning spheres with arrows on them! hop on top of such, and go for a ride! think you can use them to your advantage for getting through this cave?
Not a Rip-off of an existing series called "The 8 Worlds" I swear. This is desert plains, with a TON of coins to collect.
This course includes the new SMB2 mushroom!
watch out! boomerang bros are known to guard precious treasure in this long not so dangerous bridge!
